{"hadithnumber": "1766", "arabic": "حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏حَدَّثَنَا إِسْمَاعِيل ابْنُ عُلَيَّةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَن", "grades": "{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Shuaib Al Arnaut', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Sahih - Bukhari And Muslim'}", "reference": "Book 7, Hadith 129", "international_number": "1766", "narrator_chain": ""}
